OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772409783
OL,3,CIsrael launches daylight attack on
OL,4,CIran's capital Tehran
OL,6,FIsrael launched an attack on Iran's
OL,7,Fcapital, Tehran, on Saturday morning
OL,8,Fas reports emerged that the US were
OL,9,Finvolved in the strikes.
OL,11,FThe first apparent strikes happened
OL,12,Fnear the offices of Ayatollah Ali
OL,13,FKhamenei, while witnesses in Iran told
OL,14,Fnews agencies that further explosions
OL,15,Fhad rocked the capital, Tehran. It was
OL,16,Fnot immediately clear whether the 86-
OL,17,Fyear-old Khamenei, who has not been
OL,18,Fseen publicly in days as tensions with
OL,19,Fthe US grew, had been in his offices
OL,20,Fat the time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
