OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772409783
OL,3,CIsrael launches daylight attack on
OL,4,CIran's capital Tehran
OL,6,FA smoke cloud could be seen rising
OL,7,Ffrom an area of southern Tehran on
OL,8,FSaturday. Iranian state television
OL,9,Facknowledged the blast, without
OL,10,Fproviding more details.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
