OL,3,CIsrael launches daylight attack on
OL,4,CIran's capital Tehran
OL,6,FAccording to the Associated Press news
OL,7,Fagency, the United States is
OL,8,Fparticipating in the Israeli strikes
OL,9,Fagainst Iran, although there has been
OL,10,Fno official statement from Washington.
OL,11,FAssociated Press reported that a US
OL,12,Fofficial and a person familiar with
OL,13,Fthe operation said the US is
OL,14,Fparticipating in the Israeli strikes.
OL,15,FThey spoke on condition of anonymity
OL,16,Fto detail sensitive military
OL,17,Foperations, AP said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
