OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772409783
OL,3,CIsrael launches daylight attack on
OL,4,CIran's capital Tehran
OL,6,FThe US has been gathering a massive
OL,7,Ffleet of aircraft and warships in the
OL,8,Fregion for several weeks. On Friday,
OL,9,Fthe US urged its citizens to leave
OL,10,FIsrael as the threat of strikes grew.
OL,12,FIran and Israel have closed their
OL,13,Fairspace, while mobile services have
OL,14,Fbeen cut in Iran.
OL,16,FIsrael's defence minister, Israel
OL,17,FKatz, said a state of emergency had
OL,18,Fbeen declared across Israel. Sirens
OL,19,Fsounded across Israel at the time of
OL,20,Fthe attack on Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
