OL,3,CIsrael launches daylight attack on
OL,4,CIran's capital Tehran
OL,6,FThe Israeli military said that the
OL,7,F"proactive alert to prepare the public
OL,8,Ffor the possibility of missiles being
OL,9,Flaunched toward the state of Israel."
OL,11,FTensions between the United States and
OL,12,FIran remained high after their latest
OL,13,Ftalks in Geneva on Thursday failed to
OL,14,Freach a breakthrough, and as American
OL,15,Fforces gather in the region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
