OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772409783
OL,3,CIsrael launches daylight attack on
OL,4,CIran's capital Tehran
OL,6,FOn Friday, US President Donald Trump
OL,7,Fsaid he was "not happy" with the way
OL,8,FIran is negotiating in the nuclear
OL,9,Ftalks, but indicated he would give
OL,10,Fthem more time to reach a deal to
OL,11,Favert another war in the Middle East.
OL,13,FIran and the United States held hours
OL,14,Fof indirect negotiations over Tehran's
OL,15,Fnuclear programme in Geneva this week,
OL,16,Fbut walked away without a deal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
