OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772409783
OL,3,CIsrael launches daylight attack on
OL,4,CIran's capital Tehran
OL,6,FTrump once again warned Iran against
OL,7,Fpursuing a nuclear weapons programme
OL,8,Fduring his State of the Union address
OL,9,Fon Tuesday, referring to the US
OL,10,Fstrikes on Iranian nuclear sites in
OL,11,FJune last year.
OL,13,F"My preference is to solve this
OL,14,Fproblem through diplomacy - but one
OL,15,Fthing is certain. I will never allow
OL,16,Fthe world's number one sponsor of
OL,17,Fterror, which they are by far, to have
OL,18,Fa nuclear weapon," the president said
OL,19,Fduring his address.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
