CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772409783
OL,3,CIsrael launches daylight attack on
OL,4,CIran's capital Tehran
OL,6,FBefore the Genevan negotiations ended,
OL,7,FIranian state television reported that
OL,8,FTehran was determined to continue
OL,9,Fenriching uranium, rejected proposals
OL,10,Fto transfer it abroad and sought the
OL,11,Flifting of international sanctions.
OL,13,FIranians have been watching the
OL,14,Fbuildup with growing concern, with
OL,15,Fmany fearing the outbreak of a war
OL,16,Fcould surpass Iran's bloody 1980s
OL,17,Fconflict with Iraq.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
