OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772409783
OL,3,CIsrael launches daylight attack on
OL,4,CIran's capital Tehran
OL,6,FThe nation is still reeling from its
OL,7,Fdevastating 12-day war with Israel in
OL,8,FJune and last month's protests, which
OL,9,Fled to thousands of people being
OL,10,Fkilled and arrested.
OL,12,FThe US-based Human Rights Activist
OL,13,FNews Agency said 7,000 had died in the
OL,14,Fprotests, although the true toll is
OL,15,Flikely to be much higher. Iran's
OL,16,Fgovernment said 3,117 people had been
OL,17,Fkilled in its only death toll on
OL,18,FJanuary 21.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
